    benefitsTitle: 'Benefits of Peptide Therapy',
    benefits: [
      'Personalized metabolic support: selected peptides may complement weight and body-composition strategies.',
      'Recovery-focused care: some protocols target tissue repair pathways and inflammation management when clinically appropriate.',
      'Sleep and restoration support: in selected patients, peptide plans may help improve recovery-related sleep quality.',
      'Hormonal and sexual wellness support: when indicated, peptides can complement broader hormone and sexual health programs.',
      'Integrated treatment planning: best outcomes usually come from combining peptides with nutrition, exercise, and medical supervision.',
      'Continuous clinical monitoring: dosing and protocols are adjusted over time based on response, tolerance, and goals.'
